# The `MCPseudoProbe` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

Instances of this class represent a pseudo probe instance for a pseudo probe table entry, which is created during a machine instruction is assembled and uses an address from a temporary label created at the current address in the current section. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

Instances of this class represent a pseudo probe instance for a pseudo probe table entry, which is created during a machine instruction is assembled and uses an address from a temporary label created at the current address in the current section.
